latestIgtvVideos.title: We are all in this together 🖤
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We are never as alone as we feel. From the United States to across the nations & into Canada, we ALL share in these uncertain times we’re facing TOGETHER. Times that are calling for unity, strength, love, understanding, and being ONE. Whether friends & family are near or far, we can always count on one another to be there for us in a time of need. I couldn’t be more thankful for such an amazing group of friends who’ve helped piece this beautiful vision of mine together. Love to all! ⁣
A bunch of my mama friends and I came together to create this video! We hope it brightens your day! ✨You can catch me and my little babes at the 4:11 mark ✨⁣⁣
⁣
🌟A super extra special thank you goes out to @benleemusic for granting us full permission of rights to use his song: We’re All In This Together 💞 Artist/Musician: Ben Lee - New West Records. Videography Done By: @life.with.twins.plus2 ⁣⁣

The month of June forever changed me and as much as I tried not to let it define me, It did. It changed how I live, how I love and how I will spend the rest of my life. For so long I looked back and kept thinking that I have spent years living without you, yearning for the time that I felt was stolen from me; yet I’ve come to accept that I’ve lived all these years with so much of you. You are always in my forefront and show up in ways that I cannot describe.

Happy Heavenly Birthday to my sweet little girl Madison who made me a Mama🤍
.
.
.
.
#griefandloss #momof3 #mymotherhood #lifeafterloss #motherhoodjourney
